data.description: Beautiful 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom home in Bella Vista with a new roof! This house is move-in ready and has a ton of room for a growing family! The extra living room downstairs could make a mother-in-law suite, man cave, kids playroom, or anything else that you'd like. Enjoy the beauty of Bella Vista with all the trails, golf courses, lakes, and parks! This home has a unique opportunity with an assumable loan so you can get a cheaper interest rate than what the banks are currently offering!
